{
  "text": "The lower extremity metrics and their relation with system measures [CITATION_1] ) are shown in Figure 1 . All metrics, shown in Figure 1 , were realized by evaluating the heel positions and by calculating the timing values of stance and swing during gait, utilizing a step detection algorithm [CITATION_2] . Each metric is determined within a selected time window.",
